{"tid":468462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】港版電動+石油氣的士曝光","createTime":"2017-11-14T11:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T11:16:59.000Z","uid":28366,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"57dd8121cff8b04b11cd0e5c12aa3a5cfbfa3457","tid":468462,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:42:18.000Z","msg":"本港的士即將步入混能車時代，佔據本港逾90%的士市場的豐田汽車（TOYOTA），旗下石油氣金豐4座位的士將於兩個月內停產。代理商計劃引入新款混能的士來港，新車近日已送抵本港，「真身」在網上曝光！社交網站群組「的士司機資訊網」流傳多張新款的士，在葵涌貨櫃碼頭停泊圖片，新車外觀與現時使用車款完全不同。<br />\n<br />\n豐田的士代理商皇冠車行確認，該批新車是計劃引入香港的混能的士，車輛送抵香港，準備進行車輛類型評定測試。發言人指，引入新車需向多個政府部門提出申請，目前仍在提交文件階段，隨後亦有待接受運輸署的車輛類型評定。新車採用石油氣及電力混合推動，當電力足夠或塞車時的低車速環境，會以電力推動馬達行車。新車每公升石油氣量可行走19.4公里，較傳統石油氣的士每升約9公里，聲稱慳一半。<br />\n新混能的士可載4名乘客，同時採用無障礙設計，附設電動趟門及斜台，輪椅可直接上落。接載輪椅設計時，後座仍可另坐2名乘客。皇冠車行發言人又指，新車售價目前未定，初步估算每部約30餘萬元，承認較傳統石油氣的士25.3萬元貴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171114/large/1510650896_9d85.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171114%2Flarge%2F1510650896_9d85.png&h=470a37fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171114/large/1510648533_468d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171114%2Flarge%2F1510648533_468d.jpg&h=12cd9842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171114/large/1510648567_0254.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171114%2Flarge%2F1510648567_0254.jpg&h=4b8c5bd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171114/large/1510648663_025b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171114%2Flarge%2F1510648663_025b.jpg&h=0901a17e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171114/large/1510648695_cdd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171114%2Flarge%2F1510648695_cdd7.jpg&h=d2c92fe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171114/large/1510648741_2238.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171114%2Flarge%2F1510648741_2238.jpg&h=de582435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171114/57457384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171114%2F57457384&d=S2VsF1gsdwE4WwX7sjruNzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=f0013c9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171114%2F57457384&h=47a76c64\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171114/57457384</a>"},{"pid":"c67fe27c62637c7ba4e054bae172884cfb880a05","tid":468462,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:56:18.000Z","msg":"幾型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747176f9281fb74df37eab2a2c080bf919196bf3","tid":468462,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:09:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1895264b84309d83ec18cb34d01db75536c37f33","tid":468462,"uid":17846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:16:46.000Z","msg":"無的士牌買唔買得？"},{"pid":"65ebe024d4be3e6c07541e4289c3723c0363c8bb","tid":468462,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T13:43:37.000Z","msg":"冇位放行李<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70059db686bc0cab354341376545604e50